---
title: Double Honey-Soy Pork & Eggplant Salad Bowl with Avocado & Japanese Dressing
description: Have you ever seen a salad as bright and colourful as this one? Cabbage and pickled carrot make up the base of this bowl, topped off with creamy avocado, tender Asian-spiced pork and crispy cubes of eggplant. This dish is already bursting with flavour, but go on, add a drizzle of Japanese dressing - you know you want to!
